# Data Professional Survey Breakdown - Power BI Project

## 📊 Project Overview
This project analyzes survey data from data professionals to uncover insights about salaries, job roles, tools used, and overall job satisfaction across the data industry.

The dashboard provides an interactive and visual breakdown of key trends, helping understand the current state of the data field.

## 🛠 Tools Used
- Power BI
- Excel (Data Cleaning)

## 📈 Key Features
- Interactive dashboard with filters and slicers
- Salary analysis by job title and country
- Visualization of popular programming languages
- Work-life balance and job satisfaction insights
- Comparison between different roles in the data field

## 🔍 Insights
- Identifies the highest-paying roles in data careers
- Highlights the most commonly used tools and languages
- Shows trends in job satisfaction among data professionals
- Provides a clear comparison across countries and experience levels

